description:
Site back and relax with this stress relief session. Unwind and let go. 

This is a single hypnosis session designed to help you feel calm and comfortable with all of the things you have to do. It helps you to let go of things that are out of your control. It helps you to stay focused, even in the most stressful times of your life. 

Use this app if you are severely stressed at work, or at home, or for any reason. It is important to note that not only bad situations are stressful. Stress happens when big changes happen. So use this app if you are going through any big changes. Use this app if you simply need to unwind and relax. Use this app to completely let go of all stress in your life.
